editorialNotes.standard: On movie night we like to dim the lights, pop the popcorn, and check out MUBI. It puts an arthouse theater at our fingertips, adding a new film every day from an eclectic library of stunning world cinema. The simple interface makes it a pleasure to discover cult classics, eye-opening documentaries, and hard-to-find dramas we might\u2019ve missed.

editorialNotes.standard: Dodge dangers and knock around monsters in this action-packed runner.

ios.subtitle: Control Mario with just a tap!

editorialNotes.standard: He's here! We're all about pulling off stylish moves with a single tap, thanks to super-simple, one-touch controls. But collecting all the pink coins? That takes skill. With tons of unlocks (including Luigi!), you\u2019ll be playing this one long after you reach the final flagpole.
editorialNotes.tagline: Can you collect all the coins?

editorialNotes.short: Costumes and special events are waiting for you.

editorialNotes.standard: Presented as a holotable full of Star Wars champions, Galaxy of Heroes lets you form a team and leap into thrilling turn-based battles. Playing as Luke Skywalker, Boba Fett, Ahsoka Tano and other characters from the films and animated series, you\u2019ll need smart tactics to beat enemy squads. Missions take you from Hoth to Tatooine to Imperial ships\u2014and gorgeous graphics make every sabre slash and blaster shot look spectacular. Even when you\u2019re not fighting, though, the piles of unlockable characters, gear and abilities ensure you\u2019ll have plenty to do.
editorialNotes.short: Defeat Jabba the Hut and collect your favourite Star Wars emojis.

editorialNotes.standard: If you can imagine it, you can create it\u2014anything from monolithic towers to cavernous rollercoasters. That\u2019s the idea that sparked a world-building phenomenon in Mojang\u2019s amazing Minecraft. Since the game's release on the App Store, a steady stream of meaningful updates has kept this cube-filled universe fun, fresh and jam-packed with exciting features.
editorialNotes.short: Check out special Star Wars skin packs!

editorialNotes.standard: An \u201980s Megatron goes toe to toe with Michael Bay\u2019s Optimus Prime\u2014and we can\u2019t get enough. Kabam\u2019s brawler is a Transformers fan\u2019s dream, letting us collect and battle bots from more than 30 years of lore, including films, cartoons and comics. The fights look fantastic and control beautifully (complete with Tekken-style sidesteps), and we\u2019re digging everything from upgrading our bots to tackling story quests full of awesome characters.
editorialNotes.short: Test the mettle of your metal

editorialNotes.name: Learn a new language (or 30)
editorialNotes.short: Discover how Duolingo makes the world more accessible.

editorialNotes.standard: With its friendly approach and awesome updates, Duolingo\u2019s long been one of our favorite apps for learning another language. Its secret: making the process genuinely fun. Engaging mini-games test your reading, writing, and speaking skills, and joining a club (where you can encourage and compete with others) adds a great social element. Bonus: all those languages and games are available for free!
editorialNotes.short: Learn a new language. Join a club, chat with bots, and get reminders to practice.
